a basic 2D array of bytes? eg, data.b[wid,hit] If this is the case
then WritePixelArray8_ will work good. Anotherpiint to consider is
your buffer should have a width divisable by 16. The function works
with other sizes but the actual buffer is always rounded up to
the nearest 16bytes. Unless you're happy with understanding how the
data is stored you're better off using 16pixel widths.

